text: Gordon Henry (born 21 June 1954) is a Canadian rower. He competed in two events at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Summerside, Prince Edward Island Category:Sportspeople from Prince Edward Island
